 7th hammer server, im a GREAT guild and playin a Necro....lol oh well.<br>   <br> <p>~THUUG LYFE~~n3cr0m4nc3r~  Ghost Blanke"All yer corpse are belong to me" </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub43.ezboard.com/ufellwarre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fellwarre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle> 2    Poster<BR><TABLE WIDTH=83 HEIGHT=7 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR HEIGHT=5><TD WIDTH=2 BGCOLOR=#ffff00></TD><TD WIDTH=15 BGCOLOR=#ffff00></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15 BGCOLOR=#ffff00></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15 BGCOLOR=#ffff00></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH=2></TD></TR><TR HEIGHT=2><TD WIDTH=2 BGCOLOR=#000080></TD><TD WIDTH=15 BGCOLOR=#000080></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222><TD WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH=1 BGCOLOR=#222222></TD><TD WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH=2></TD></TR></TABLE></span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/17/02 12:11:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=205.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Your First Day Of Playing Everquest (Share Your Stories!</span><hr size=1> My first character was a Half-Elf bard.  I couldn't find the 'sing' button, and thought it was pretty weak that I was a bard and couldn't sing, so I quit him and started a Druid named Fellwarre <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>The rest, as they say, is history. <p><IMG SRC=http://www.eqwolf.com/sigs/fell.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub43.e