 but I figured there'd be a lot of those around.  I wanted to be a little different, a little specialized, so I chose a Magician.<br><br>Wandering around Erudin I found another player, a fellow Erudite killing an NPC in a bar.  I thought that was a bit odd.  He had a friend with him who looked like a skeleton.  That was pretty odd too.  I tried talking to the Erudite, but he didn't really want to talk to me.  His skeleton friend ignored me.<br><br>Using the maps in the back of the manual I made it to the newbie grounds.  I wandered around some, got wicked lost, died, rinse and repeat.  Some nice person found me and grouped with me, told me a lot of useful stuff.  When I told him I didn't have any containers, he gave me a backpack!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><html><center><table style=filter:glow(color=Blue><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=505 STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION: NONE" TARGET="_blank"><font size=2 color=White face=Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica><b>&nbsp;Balasarius NoxDominus&nbsp;</b></font></a></table></center><center><font size=1 color=Blue face=Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica><b>Arch Mage of <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/bemeraldflame STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION: NONE"><font size=1 color=00FF00 face=Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica>&lt;Emerald Flame&gt;</font></a></b></font></center><font size=1>&nbsp<center><table style=filter:glow(color=Red><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4619 STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION: NONE" TARGET="_blank"><font size=2 color=FFFF99 face=Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica><b>&nbsp;Zhentar&nbsp;</b> </font></a></table></center><center><font size=1 color=Red face=Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica><b>53rd Disciple of the Lost Circle</b></font></center><font size=1>&nbsp<center><font size=2 color=Black face=