omeone who knew nothing about the game.  <br>  So I whacked my way to level 4.  Saved enough money to buy a few spells, one of which was Summon Elementalkin: Water.  Well I thought this was an elemental spell like in Diablo, you cast it at enemy and this elemental charges and hurts the enemy.  So I find a spider and cast the spell and nothing happen, so I run to the spider and notice something is following me, so naturally not wanting to die I figure I will run to guards and they will kill this thing.  Not really knowing the zone I spent about 10 minutes running and jumping with this thing following me.  At this point I have done /shout HELP, /say HELP, /yell with people looking stangely at me as I kept running around.<br>  Then I ran unto a skeleton which attacked me, so I figured I am bound to die, so I stopped and saw the blue blob that was chasing me was fighting the skeleton now, didn't take long to realize who Jabober was when I saw the infamous &quot;Taunting Attacker Master&quot;...  to be young again... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br> <p><table><tr><td align="right" valign="bottom" style=""><a  href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=84260" target="_magelo_" style="text-decoration: none;"><font style="font-family: Arial Black; font-size: 16px; color: red;"><b>Glasya</b></font></a></td><td><big><a href="http://www.foreverquest.com/" style="text-decoration: none;"><font style="font-family: Arial Narrow; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255,0,0);">&lt;Fires Within&gt;</font></a></big></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub43.ezboard.com/uszacharmore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Szach Armore</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle> 4    Poster<BR><TABLE WIDTH=83 HEIGHT=7 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR HEIGHT=5><TD WIDTH=