and those were a hard earned 24 levels!) which is when I started a character on Xegony to play with some friends I had made along the way.<br><br> <p><B>Mdiria L'Soduire<BR><A HREF="http://eq.forgedsouls.org/">Forged Souls</A></B><BR><BR><I>Quote of the moment:</I><BR><IMG SRC="http://eq.forgedsouls.org/images/quote/randpic.php"></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.showMessageRange?topicID=205.topic&start=21&stop=34>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=205.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=205.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=205.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=205.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.threadControl?topicID=205.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=205.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub43.ezboard.com/f7thhammerfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=205.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub43.ezboard.com/BBSForum.